Pengetahuan Responsinve Design dan Media Query

=====================

Untuk media query:
@media (max-width: {width})
@media (min-width: {width})
@media (orientation: portrait) dan @media (orientation: landscape)

=================================

code nya

=============================

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Responsive Design Example</title>
    <style>
      /* Default styles */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .box {
        flex: 1 1 200px;
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* Styles for screens smaller than 768px (e.g., smartphones) */
      @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .container {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 10px;
        }

        .box {
          flex: 0 0 auto;
        }
      }

      /* Styles for screens larger than 1200px (e.g., desktops) */
      @media (min-width: 1200px) {
        .container {
          max-width: 1200px;
          margin: 0 auto;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Box 1</h2>
        <p>This is the first box.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Box 2</h2>
        <p>This is the second box.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Box 3</h2>
        <p>This is the third box.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Box 4</h2>
        <p>This is the fourth box.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Box 5</h2>
        <p>This is the fifth box.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Box 6</h2>
        <p>This is the sixth box.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>


==============================================
